{"tid":2422937,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"女權網站批評《 Mortal Kombat 》電影沒有春麗　反被網民恥笑","createTime":"2021-02-25T14:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T14:50:18.000Z","uid":193217,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ad781a29dad66b99bf3668cb86df12644530790d","tid":2422937,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"以暴力血腥為主題的格鬥遊戲《 Mortal Kombat （真人快打）》，在日前發布了真人電影預告片，卻被女權網站 Jezebel 批評電影中沒有角色 「春麗」的出場，引來網民們恥笑。<br />\n<br />\n女權網站 Jezebel 日前發表了一篇「 Who Forgot to Invite Chun-Li to the Mortal Kombat？ 」的文章，內文提及到「在電影中的主角都是為了地球的命運而戰，為何又不將春麗從她的世界（ Realm ）邀請過來，再用她的倒旋鶴腳踢（ Spinning bird kick）將敵人擊敗？」。<br />\n<br />\n內文亦有提到《 Mortal Kombat 》女角色 Sonya Blade ，可見文章作者理應有做足功課，理應清楚春麗並非該遊戲的角色。<br />\n假如對遊戲有一定認知的玩家，就知道春麗是來自另一廠商 Capcom 《街霸》的遊戲角色，假如要將她加入到電影中，就如同「張飛打岳飛」一樣不可能發生，反被網民恥笑，圍攻文章作者「唔識扮識」。但基於內文中用不少如上方的「 Realm 」、「倒旋鶴腳踢」等要對遊戲有一定認知的字眼，內文亦有提到《 Mortal Kombat 》女角色 Sonya Blade ，加上有不少是「為踩而踩」的部分，有理由懷疑作者為煽動女權才刻意引戰，最終卻弄巧反拙，在大家眼中顯得更像蠢蛋一樣。<br />\n<br />\n在被圍攻後不久， Jezebel 在文中下方補充「 Jezebel has discovered the answer to our question about Chun Li&rsquo;s erasure, and it is that Chun Li is not part of the Mortal Kombat megaverse. Wow! 」，指他們知道春麗並非《 Mortal Kombat 》的人物，但文中可見態度依然惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/mortal-kombat-movie-does-not-have-chunli-feminist-website-is-besieged/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fmortal-kombat-movie-does-not-have-chunli-feminist-website-is-besieged%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFbTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=56cf81a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/mortal-kombat-movie-does-not-have-chunli-feminist-website-is-besieged/</a><br />\n<br />\n為奶共可以去到幾絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607f8cd459da84460f4e4dab6c89d46a34674582","tid":2422937,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://jezebel.com/who-forgot-to-invite-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjezebel.com%2Fwho-forgot-to-invite-&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFbTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=b92a81f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jezebel.com/who-forgot-to-invite-</a><br />\n正撚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9996c74f9d73ccbc056ca372b476a7174f5f6ec3","tid":2422937,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"為甚麼不把維尼從牠的世界邀請過來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3421e3b259d87d26c932ae2f6b6482ae2716acd1","tid":2422937,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:48:58.000Z","msg":"我要投訴女權點解唔叫加不知火舞<br />\n係咪歧視大波日本妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3a0c8eee23793107d371c60318c31f64e5fda0","tid":2422937,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:50:18.000Z","msg":"女權係咪歧視日本妹?<br />\n加春麗唔加不知火舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"3e3a0c8eee23793107d371c60318c31f64e5fda0","tid":2422937,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:50:18.000Z","msg":"女權係咪歧視日本妹?<br />\n加春麗唔加不知火舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"h